{{Portal|Neuroscience}} {{Infobox journal | title = Neuroinformatics | abbreviation=Neuroinformatics | cover = Neuroinformatics (journal).jpg | discipline = [[Neuroinformatics]] | publisher = [[Springer Science+Business Media|Humana Press]] | ISSN = 1539-2791 | eISSN = 1559-0089 }} '''''Neuroinformatics''''' is a [[scientific journal]] published by [[Springer Science+Business Media|Springer]] under the [[imprint (trade name)|imprint]] [[Humana Press]]. As the title indicates it publishes articles about [[neuroinformatics]].
The journal is indexed in a wide range of bibliographic databases, e.g., [[PubMed]]. The [[Thomson Reuters]] ''[[Journal Citation Reports]]'' [[impact factor]] was reported to be just above 3 in 2012,<ref>https://www.springer.com/biomed/neuroscience/journal/12021</ref> while [[Google Scholar]] reported its [[h-index|h5-index]] to be 20 in December 2013.<ref>https://scholar.google.com/citations?hl=en&view_op=search_venues&vq=neuroinformatics</ref> It has 3 [[Editors-in-Chief]]s: [[Giorgio A. Ascoli]], [[Erik De Schutter]] and [[David N. Kennedy]].
A competing journal is ''[[Frontiers in Neuroinformatics]]'' published by [[Frontiers Media]]. That journal is fully [[open access]]. ''Neuroinformatics'' also has an open access option.
